data.title: Actress and Author Amber Tamblyn on Brittany Murphy, Love, and Her Favorite Poem
meta_keywords: what to do a the miami book fair
data.meta_description: Amber Tamblyn is, in many ways, a mystery. An actress, a director, a poet, a performance artist (she recently embarked on a motorcycle poetry tour across Texas with fellow poet Derrick Brown, dubbed Lazers of Sexcellence 5.0) — Tamblyn has been working since the tender age of 13. From turns in The Sisterhood...
